            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-04/kewenzhezuohelaixianglingziyoushibao.jpg?VersionId=fh0aCSeoIg4j3ZgQ2jBHQURKxOWloMV_&amp;itok=0idV5bIs" title="民众党主席柯文哲（左）表明，将针对自己的不当言论，私下与赖香伶讲就好。（自由时报）" alt="民众党主席柯文哲（左）表明，将针对自己的不当言论，私下与赖香伶讲就好。（自由时报）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-04/kewenzhezuohelaixianglingziyoushibao.jpg?VersionId=fh0aCSeoIg4j3ZgQ2jBHQURKxOWloMV_&amp;itok=0idV5bIs" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
